2004-03-16  Angus Leeming  <angus.leeming@btopenworld.com>

	* quickdoc-xhtml.diff: add a 'copyright' tag to enable the writer
	to define a copyright notice that will appear on the bottom of
	every page. Define a "__TOP_LEVEL_DIR__" tag that is substituted
	for "." in index.html and for ".." in all other generated pages.

	Important note: the contents of the 'copyright' block are raw html,
	not quickdoc markup.

	* doc/yac.txt: add a copyright notice.

