2004-03-11  Angus Leeming  angus.leeming@btopenworld.com

	* Release of YAC version 1.0.

2004-03-11  Angus Leeming  angus.leeming@btopenworld.com

	* quickdoc-xhtml.diff: added the ability to specify the "alt"
	field in an image. Eg, [$smiley.gif ;-)] is converted to
	<img src="smiley.gif" alt=":-)"></img>. If the field is not
	specified, then it is output as empty. (To not output any alt
	field is invalid XHTML.)

	* yac.txt: add alt fields to the two images input in the text,
	smiley.gif and alert.gif.
